name: Mrs Herskin Gift Voucher
description:
If you want to treat someone to a special gift give them a Mrs Herskin gift voucher to spend on any item in our online shop.
Gift voucher allow recipients to select their favorite items and use the prepaid amount on the voucher towards their purchase.

The beautifully packed and designed gift cards can be sent direct to the recipient or posted to your address so you can give it to them in person. Please contact us at shop@mrsherskin.com for orders and details! 
You can also order a Mrs Herskin virtual gift voucher which will arrive directly into your recipient's inbox. In this way there will be no shipping charge. Perfect for last minute present. 

Gift vouchers are available in denominations of 50 EUR, 70 EUR, 100 EUR, 400 EUR. Other values also available on request.

Redeemable only for goods at mrsherskin.bigcartel.com online store. Just send your coupon code to shop@mrsherskin.com
Valid for 18 months from issue date. 
Not redeemable for cash, cannot be replaced if lost.
